stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: m = sha256()
    q_init --> q_iter: for request in requests
    q_iter --> q_hash: has next request
    q_hash --> q_update: digest = sha256(request).digest()
    q_update --> q_iter: m.update(digest)
    q_iter --> q_return: no more requests
    q_return --> [*]: return m.digest()
